Uncertain. Attested meaning as those who have been beaten/broken/afflicted does not fit. Root is related to beat/strike, so perhaps "attackers."

Unknown. Apparently "ungodly mockers of the bread-cake." Many go with something like "ungodly mockers at a feast."
